(8383, 155793, '名為自我的那些', '「nowhere或許是未知的徬徨卻也是Now Here時時刻刻 每個當下的 存 在 」\n\nnowhere樂團結識於台中，音樂以清亮女聲及木吉他為主線，富旋律性的電吉他SOLO、BASS 和鼓交織的明快節奏組成。創作靈感以對自我的辯證與探索、社會事件的反思為主，清新之下帶著反叛精神、以柔中帶剛的搖滾樂，記錄著每個生活當下。\n\n首張創作EP「名為自我的那些」選曲的3首歌主題皆來自對自我的辯證，無論是在身分轉換之中、還是他人眼光與自我期待中，或成長找尋定位過程中，而加上是首張EP， 有種以自己為出發的概念，故名為《名為自我的那 些》，「那些」則是期待每個聽眾可以因為聽完歌曲，而透過反思自行填入(進而完整/重整了自我)。 \n\nNoWhere means "in the middle of nowhere"\nand meanwhile implies "now we are here\nat every moment we exist". \n  \nNowhere band comes from Taichung, Taiwan, and is composed of\nvocalist, acoustic guitarist, electronic guitarist, bassist,\nand drumist. Our music features in our clear and sweet female\nvoice, the beautiful melody of electronic guitar, and the\ngrooving rhythm of bass and drums. \n \nThe inspiration for our songs comes from the process of\nself-exploration and from our reflections on social events.\n\nNowhere Band cares deeply about social issues and tries to live in\nthe moment and to be a gentle rebel in the society with an iron hand\nin a velvet glove.\n', '2015-03-01 00:00:00', 0, 2, 5, '', '', 0, '', 1, 0, '2015-02-17 14:12:13', '2015-03-01 00:00:03', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(8384, 83261, '#001/S', '「 #001/S 」\n此單曲創作靈感源自日常生活。\n\n生活它真實、虛幻、偶爾滑稽有趣。\n做好人，過好每一天。\n帶節奏般完成待完成的事，再好不過。\n---------------------------------------------------\n「 #001/S 」\nThis single is inspired from daily bits and pieces.\n\nEveryday life seems real, at the same time surreal, and interesting at times.\nBe who you are and live the days.\nNothing could be better than being in the smooth, tempo-like flow of progressing on what you are working on.\n\n', '2015-02-18 00:00:00', 0, 4, 7, '日安', '', 0, '', 1, 0, '2015-02-18 01:12:58', '2015-02-18 02:41:05', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
