(8396, 338292, 'Martin Tungevaag 馬汀徒威 - Vidorra', 'Vidorra是西班牙文,意思為~"好生活(good life)"\n\n來自挪威,獲選為"MTV歐洲音樂獎最佳挪威藝人,"21歲的創作藝人"馬汀徒威",繼2014年夏天橫掃全球的成名神曲"Wicked Wonderland"之後,最新推出的EDM單曲.\n"馬汀徒威"說他的創作動機就是:享受生活,走出舒適圈,這就是Vidorra的意思!!\n\n跳動的節拍,薩克斯風性感旋律與女生歌聲,絕對讓您對無法坐著聽完!!!\n\n\nFollowing on from the hit of the 2014 summer "Wicked Wonderland" (platinum in Norway, gold in Germany, top 10 in France, #2 in Sweden & more than 15 mio views on Youtube) the Norwegian shooting star Martin Tungevaag now presents his new single "Vidorra"….\n… and it is another incredibly catchy, uplifting track.\n"It''s all about enjoying life, opening up and leaving your comfort zone, that''s what Vidorra is, that''s how you can be Vidorra!" the 21 year old explains.\n\nThe pulsating beat, fantastic sax melody and vocals add up to an unforgettable song!\n', '2015-02-27 00:00:00', 0, 4, 3, 'Martin Tungevaag  ', '', 0, '', 1, 0, '2015-02-27 19:04:56', '2015-02-27 20:00:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
